Class CriticalityLevel

java.lang.Object
WorkLoad.CriticalityLevel
public class CriticalityLevel extends Object
Represents a qualitative criticality level used in the workload model.

The higher the numeric value of criticalityLevel, the higher the criticality (integrated from the original inline comment: "When the value of criticalityLevel is higher, which means it has more higher criticality level."). This lightweight value object is typically attached to tasks or jobs to distinguish importance or assurance level in mixed-criticality analyses.
